## ğŸ¨ Customization

### Theme Colors
In admin panel: **Settings â†’ Theme Primary Color**
- Cyan (default)
- Pink
- Amber
- Green

### Matrix Effect
Customize via admin:
- Enable/disable matrix rain
- Change characters (supports Unicode/Meitei script)
- Adjust opacity and speed

