## ğŸ”§ Development

### Clone & Setup
```bash
git clone https://github.com/Okramjimmy/ojsTerminalBio.git
cd ojsTerminalBio
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
pip install -e .
```

### Run locally
```bash
ojsterminalbio init-db
ojsterminalbio runserver
```

